weka.dl4j.interpretability

Class AbstractCNNSaliencyMapGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • weka.dl4j.interpretability.AbstractCNNSaliencyMapGenerator
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ScoreCAM

    public abstract class AbstractCNNSaliencyMapGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
    Generic class for a saliency map generator. Only implemented by ScoreCAM currently so some fields may need to be refactored when implementing a new generator method. This method should be kept as free of Weka classes as possible, so that this can all be refactored into the DL4J package (which doesn't have WEKA as a dependency).

      • processImage

        public abstract void processImage(java.io.File imageFile)
        Main processing entrypoint. Takes an image as input, and performs the necessary processing on it. Note that this is performed separately to the actual saliency map generation. This method should only perform the expensive one-time processing on an image.
        Parameters:
        imageFile - File to process into saliency map.
